* nddiff --brief
    ndquery --list style output, show only root item in changed substructure

* nddiff --ctx-text <num>

* nddiff --ctx-struct <num>

* nddiff --patch
    1. Visualize patch if one argument used
    2. Make small possible diff (patch) when two arguments used

* ndpatch --path <path>
    patch only specified parts

* ndpatch --ignore <path>
    don't patch specified parts

* ndproc
    Processing tool

* ndquery --delete|--ignore <path>
    Remove desired parts

